The '''Moluccan drongo-cuckoo''' ('''''Surniculus musschenbroeki''''') is a species of [[cuckoo]]. It is found on [[Sulawesi]], [[Buton]], [[Obira]], [[Bacan]] and [[Halmahera]] islands in [[Indonesia]].

